title: Wrong documantation for core::arch::{x86, x86_64}::_mm_insert_ps

### Location
[x86](https://doc.rust-lang.org/core/arch/x86/fn._mm_insert_ps.html), [x86_64](https://doc.rust-lang.org/core/arch/x86_64/fn._mm_insert_ps.html)

### Summary
The documentation says "Select a single value in `a` to store at some position in `b`, ...", but it actually works the other way around.
